   377тЖТ## Caveats
   382тЖТBy default, `input-otp` handles password managers for you.
   383тЖТThe password manager badges should be automatically shifted to the right side.
   384тЖТ
   385тЖТHowever, if you still want to block password managers, please disable the `pushPasswordManagerStrategy` and then manually block each PWM.
   386тЖТ
   387тЖТ```diff
   388тЖТ<OTPInput
   389тЖТ  // First, disable library's built-in strategy
